Name: Base Station License, Approval, Liberty Express Car & Limo Services Inc., Queens
Title: A Local Law in relation to the approval of a determination by the Taxi and Limousine Commission to approve an application by Liberty Express Car & Limo Services, Inc. also known as Liberty Express Car & Limo Service, Inc. also known as Liberty Express Car & Limo Service Inc. for a license to operate a new base station in the borough of Queens.
Text:
Be it enacted by the Council as follows:

      Section one.  The determination by the Taxi and Limousine Commission to approve an application by Liberty Express Car & Limo Services, Inc. also known as Liberty Express Car & Limo Service, Inc. also known as Liberty Express Car & Limo Service Inc. for a license to operate a new base station at 94-14 Sutphin Boulevard in the borough of Queens is hereby approved. 
      ï¿½2. This local law shall take effect immediately.
